name: 1 hour Skype lesson.
description:
A 1 hour Skype lesson with Josh, teaching you everything you want to know and learn in magic.

Please fill out a contact form* with the prefered times and days, and someone will get back to you. 

*http://www.joshmaddocksmagic.com/consultant.html

name: One hour live lesson*
description:
Josh has taught various people over the years from his friends to other professional magicians he has taught them all, 
and now, you could learn too!

If you are interested in having a lesson with Josh, please send him a detailed email of what you would like to learn over the hour(s)
so when you book a lesson you will know what to expect. If not, Josh will have some tricks prepared for your lesson. 


*Subject to location, Josh is currently based in Northamptonshire and is able to travel provided expenses are paid. and therefore costs are subject to change.

name: Bicycle rider back (blue/red)
